OL,7,FZoe Hughes spoke to Granada Reports
OL,8,FPresenter Katie Walderman about her
OL,9,Fcalls for an overhaul of domestic
OL,10,Fviolence laws
OL,12,FThis report contains content some
OL,13,Fviewers might find distressing.
OL,15,FA woman who suffered a catalogue of
OL,16,Finjuries after being attacked by her
OL,17,Fboyfriend, is calling for an overhaul
OL,18,Fof domestic violence laws after he was
OL,19,Freleased from jail two weeks after
OL,20,Fbeing sentenced.
