OL,3,CDomestic abuse victim left with a
OL,4,Cbroken eye socket calls for tougher
OL,5,Csentencing
OL,7,FZoe Hughes, 26, from Birkenhead, was
OL,8,Fleft with permanent nerve damage to
OL,9,Fher face and a broken eye socket,
OL,10,Fafter the brutal attack at the hands
OL,11,Fof her partner, Declan Gateley.
OL,13,FHe was jailed for 28 months, but was
OL,14,Ffreed just two weeks later due to
OL,15,Fprison overcrowding.
OL,17,FZoe Hughes needed metal plates to
OL,18,Freconstruct her face, and was also
OL,19,Fleft with a broken nose, and a large
OL,20,Fhaematoma behind her eye, which
OL,21,Frequired emergency surgery.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
