OL,5,Csentencing
OL,7,F"I just remember waking up, and just
OL,8,Frealised I couldn't open my eye," said
OL,9,FZoe. "My eye was completely swollen."
OL,11,FShe says the impact of the attack has
OL,12,Fbeen devastating and she has since had
OL,13,Fto have three further surgeries.
OL,15,F"I've been put on extra medication for
OL,16,Fanxiety and depression. I can't go to
OL,17,Fsleep at night without any sort of
OL,18,Fmedication," she said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
