OL,5,Csentencing
OL,7,F"I'm still in pain every single day.
OL,8,FInstead of taking my handbag to work,
OL,9,FI take two packs of painkillers and a
OL,10,Fhot water bottle because it is the
OL,11,Fonly way I get through."
OL,13,FZoe's attack in April 2024 came
OL,14,Fcompletely out of the blue. She had
OL,15,Fbeen on a night out with her partner
OL,16,Fthat evening and had never faced
OL,17,Fviolence before in her 18 month
OL,18,Frelationship.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
