OL,3,CDomestic abuse victim left with a
OL,4,Cbroken eye socket calls for tougher
OL,5,Csentencing
OL,7,FDeclan Gateley pleaded guilty and was
OL,8,Fhanded a 28-month prison sentence but
OL,9,Fdue to time spent on remand, and
OL,10,Fprison overcrowding, he was released
OL,11,Ftwo weeks later.
OL,13,FHe remains on tag until April 2025 and
OL,14,Fhas also been given a seven-year
OL,15,Frestraining order.
OL,17,FBut Zoe has called for an overhaul of
OL,18,Fdomestic violence laws and a change in
OL,19,Fthe way those who survive the abuse
OL,20,Fare treated.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
