OL,7,F"He gets to live a normal life whilst
OL,8,FI'm still dealing with the treatments
OL,9,Fand the operations," she said. "I
OL,10,Fdon't agree with the whole sentencing.
OL,12,F"The deterrents need to be a lot
OL,13,Fhigher. The whole law needs completely
OL,14,Fchanging.
OL,16,F"There's no official mechanisms for
OL,17,Fthe victims to dispute any of the
OL,18,Fcase."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
