OL,4,Cbroken eye socket calls for tougher
OL,5,Csentencing
OL,7,FZoe has also called for stricter laws
OL,8,Fto force offenders to physically be in
OL,9,Fcourt for sentencing and be made to
OL,10,Fparticipate in restorative justice.
OL,12,F"Every offender should come up to the
OL,13,Fdock, they should be forced into the
OL,14,Fcourtroom. The same for having the
OL,15,Foption to do restorative justice," she
OL,16,Fadded.
OL,18,F"If the offender says no, then that is
OL,19,Fit, the victim is left in the lurch
OL,20,Fand there's just no closure, no
OL,21,Fanswers, no nothing."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
